See [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) for the full source of truth on project conventions, stack,
and the component definition of done.

Key rules at a glance:
- No Husky, lint-staged, changesets, commitlint, or semantic-release.
- No CSS-in-JS of any kind.
- No new tooling added to the stack without explicit discussion first.
- All packages: TypeScript strict, ESM-only output via tsup.
- Lint + format: Biome only (no ESLint, no Prettier).
